<h3 class="mb-3 mt-5">Strava integration</h3>
<p>
    Tevling uses Strava as identity provider. Authenticated users are stored with basic information in
    Tevling's database. All <em>public*</em> activities uploaded to Strava by authenticated users are
    automatically synced to Tevling where parts of the activity details are stored in Tevling's database.
    We only store enough data to be able to calculate a score for a given challenge.
</p>
<p>
    <em style="font-size: 0.85rem">* Public activities includes activities with visibility set to 'Everyone' and 'Followers'.</em>
</p>

